{"tid":682568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3款萬能插頭 機電署籲勿用","createTime":"2018-05-29T03:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T03:35:06.000Z","uid":72478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb190ee5ee383127589c0e6ab2ec50f49fe7d379","tid":682568,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180526/s00028/0d0465dfa26de20c86b8bd5ffda6f90b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180526%2Fs00028%2F0d0465dfa26de20c86b8bd5ffda6f90b.jpg&h=47758e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n使用萬能插頭要注意！機電工程署近日呼籲市民切勿使用3款沒有標示製造商名稱或商標，並有潛在危險的萬能插頭。3款萬能插頭均印有「TRAVEL UNIVERSAL ADAPTOR」字樣、有不規則形狀的插孔及可伸出多種插腳。<br />\n<br />\n該3款萬能插頭沒有按《電氣產品（安全）規例》的要求標示製造商名稱或商標。另外，使萬能插頭任何一組插腳時，其他插腳亦會帶電，構成觸電危險。市民不應購買任何沒有標示製造商名稱或商標的電氣產品，如有疑問或舉報懷疑違規情況，可致電1823查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：政府新聞公報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1527243683408&amp;issue=20180526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1527243683408%26issue%3D20180526&d=Ymjqb4qXfs%2FskuslA%2FANxFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b8eaffb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1527243683408%26issue%3D20180526&h=457ba56d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1527243683408&amp;issue=20180526</a>"}]}